good point, I am adding PXF_CONF to the PXF script:
# Deprecated, will be removed at some point in the future.
# We keep it for backwards compatibility
export PXF_CONF=${PXF_CONF:-$PXF_HOME}

# Path to PXF_RUN directories, defaults to PXF_HOME
export PXF_RUN=${PXF_RUN:-$PXF_CONF}

